10 An Act relating to the State Department of Health;
creating the Oklahoma Rural Health Transformation
11 Program; stating purpose; designating the State
Department of Health as lead agency; allowing for the
12 Department to partner with other agencies; creating
reporting requirements; creating the Oklahoma Rural
13 Health Transformation Revolving Fund; establishing
fund at the State Department of Health; deeming the
14 funds appropriated; providing expenditure and
budgeting requirements and limitations; requiring a
15 minimum balance in the fund at the end of the
project; allowing for use of memoranda of
16 understanding; limiting scope of such memoranda;
providing for codification; and declaring an
17 emergency.
